Create UserModel

Create partition CRUD UserController with base Endpoint /user
and add next endpoints:
GET /user/:id
PATCH /user/:id -b 'email?, password?, name?, secondName?, birthDate?'
DELETE /user/:id

Create Interface for connecting AuthService with UserService that include
findByEmailWithPassword(email): id
create(id, data): id

Create UserService that implement Interface implemented above with additional methods And all needed DTO:
findById(id)
update(id, data)
delete(id)







